reviewText:
I've got a lot of these "Crazy Chicks" DVDs, which I like quite much, so I thought I'd finally try this "Midwest Invasion" one. After seeing it about half a dozen times now, I'd say it's a decent Crazy Chicks but not one of the best. The total run time is about 58 minutes, and of that about 45 minutes is spent with several girls on a farm posing, kissing each other, walking around, and so on. They're nice-looking, though just a couple are standouts. I wish at least one of them were stacked, but that's my bias. Two of the girls spray each other with garden hoses and wash off for several minutes. The girls do get totally naked and are not shy about it, so that's a plus. Nothing is censored.

Halfway through the program shifts to a strip-tease contest at some kind of park. This also has nice-looking girls, and a couple of them ARE stacked!! They only strip down to thongs, though. The strip-tease only lasts 9 minutes and we're back to the farm for more posing and such, so that's a let-down. What happened to the rest of the stripping footage? Picture quality is good and full screen, but on the farm the camerawork is a little wobbly and wandering. So overall this DVD is pretty good, I'm glad I have it, but my favorite "Crazy Chicks" are the Devil's Cove and Spring Break ones. Sadly, about all these Crazy Chicks DVDs are out of production, so get them while you can.
